title: Pepper and Corned Tuna Salad
ingredients: ['1 red pepper, julienned', '1 yellow pepper, julienned', '1/2 onion, thinly sliced', '1 (200g) tin corned tuna, drained', '1 teaspoon salt', '2 table spoons soy sauce', '1/2 teaspoon sugar', '1/3-1/2 teasppon black pepper', '1/2 teaspoon chopped garlic', '2 tablespoons sesame seeds', '2 tablespoons sesame oil']
